Value.author: Tadashi Umemura
text: Cows used to pull cars in Japan. In other words, it is a substitute for a car. The Japanese were eating fish at that time. I would never have imagined that Japanese would eat cattle. Now the cow becomes a steak. Become a hamburger. Yes, it is a milk supplier. It's a creature, but a milk factory. I don't know if milk is really nutritious. But sometimes I want to eat steak. By the way, cows are used by God in India. Sleeping in the middle of the road.But the type of cow is different. It's not like black and white but black or brown with a beard.
